---
title: Tomato & Chorizo Linguine with Parmesan & Rocket Salad
description: Golden strands of linguine combine with rich tomato paste, cream and smokey chorizo to create an elegant meal fit for only the
best. Add sharp Parmesan and a rocket salad for crunch and dinner is complete.
